&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp Spillmean treaes fler<br>
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp Shanti  strearg<br>
<br>
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp (In days of sorrow<br>
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp Leaves of fear<br>
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp Peace tomorrow<br>
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp <br>
<br>
As she finished the final descension, her voice softened into a rich, clear pianissimo.  &quot;Sham aftra rait trer&quot; (The path is clear.)  Cerres rose unsteadily.  Her legs trembled. Taking a deep breath, she followed her brother to help with his robes. <p>Cerres Swiftfyre <BR>
